## Time Investment Estimate

| Phase | Task | Time Required |
|-------|------|---------------|
| 1 | Business entity + bank | 2-3 hours (+ waiting) |
| 1 | Stripe setup + test | 1-2 hours |
| 1 | Accounting setup | 1 hour |
| 2 | Contract templates | 3-4 hours (if DIY) |
| 2 | Insurance research + purchase | 1 hour |
| 3 | Onboarding materials | 4-6 hours |
| 3 | Technical setup | 2-3 hours |
| 4 | Website + profile | 4-6 hours |
| 4 | Proposal + scripts | 2-3 hours |
| 4 | Lead generation | 2-3 hours |
| **Total** | **Pre-Client Prep** | **22-31 hours** |

**Reality:** Spread over 1-2 weeks (with waiting for approvals). Budget 1 weekend + 3-4 evenings.

