## Post-First-Client: What to Update

After your first client experience, revisit this checklist and update:

- [ ] **Onboarding process** (what took too long? what can be templated?)
- [ ] **Proposal template** (did they ask questions you didn't cover?)
- [ ] **Pricing** (was it too low? did they hesitate?)
- [ ] **Contract** (any issues? did client request changes?)
- [ ] **Technical setup** (any tools you wish you had?)

**Document:** Keep a "lessons learned" doc after each client. By client 5, you'll have a bulletproof system.

